<doc id="481991" wikidata="Q717323" url="?curid=481991" title="Lists of World War II military equipment">
<text>Lists of World War II military equipment are lists of military equipment in use during World War II (1939–1945). They include lists of aircraft, ships, vehicles, weapons, personal equipment, uniforms, and other equipment. There are aggregated military equipment lists by country, and lists of classes of equipment broken down by country or by type.

