Current members
*Alex Kapranos – lead vocals, guitar ; piano 
*Bob Hardy – bass guitar, percussion ; backing vocals 
*Julian Corrie – keyboards, synthesisers, guitar, backing vocals 
*Dino Bardot – guitar, backing vocals 
*Audrey Tait – drums, percussion 
Former members
*Paul Thomson – drums, percussion, backing and occasional lead vocals 
*Nick McCarthy – guitar, keyboards, synthesisers, backing and occasional lead vocals 


